{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And this is when something broke in me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So whatever has happened, has affected my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "This is when something broke emotionally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I shut down in some way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what actually has happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But this is the day, the event, that sort of changed me for good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "When I got up from that, my mother was coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "My father was in the hut by himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to go and see him When she came back and I got up from the meadow, I was a different person.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was-- something has broken is, I guess, the best way to describe it-- describe it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I guess whatever happened there was denied even though what has happened the next day, the policeman did not show up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "This was a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were packing to go, but we talked to a next door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he would arrange for him that he was going to take us after midnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He would take us across the river to a forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we were going to run away, take advantage of the fact that the policeman was not there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I guess the policeman was not there, because my mother bought him off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Only it wasn't money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So we took off to the woods, my father, my mother, and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I was the-- I became the leader.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I knew the-- you know, I was the know-it-all again.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
